290. BMC Public Health. 2016 Feb 9;16:128. doi: 10.1186/s12889-016-2806-6.

Absolute cardiovascular risk in a Fiji medical zone.

Gyaneshwar R(1)(2), Naidu S(3)(4), Raban MZ(5)(6), Naidu S(7), Linhart C(8), 
Morrell S(9), Tukana I(10), Taylor R(11).

Author information:
(1)Viseisei Sai Health Centre, Viseisei village, Ba Province, Fiji. 
rajat.gyaneshwar@gmail.com.
(2)Fiji School of Medicine, College of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences, 
