Years of life that could be saved from prevention of hepatocellular carcinoma.

Cucchetti A(1), Trevisani F(1), Bucci L(1), Ravaioli M(1), Farinati F(2), 
Giannini EG(3), Ciccarese F(4), Piscaglia F(1), Rapaccini GL(5), Di Marco M(6), 
